to do so i had to explicitly preserve the time zones
on the committer field, since the backend has been
committing those with "+0000" (erroneously; but i
don't want that "changed" just because i'm rebasing
because that'd just be misleading...)

so the replacement had to be altered from:

    sed s/+0000/-0000/

to

    sed '/^committer www /!s/+0000/-0000/'

using this Vim macro:

    :%s:s/+0000/-0000/:'/^committer www /!\0':

